  "instructions": [
    "1. In a bowl, whisk together olive oil, Dijon mustard, lemon juice, zest, sea salt, black pepper, and cayenne pepper to make the dressing.",
    "2. Toss the cucumber, red onion, capers, dill, and vine leaves with the dressing until everything is evenly coated.",
    "3. Gently fold in the salmon cubes, reserving a small handful for garnish.",
    "4. Plate the salad on a chilled plate, garnish with the reserved salmon and extra dill if desired, and serve immediately."
  ],
